ActionReason is a BusinessClass
    owned by la
    prefix is chgr

    Ontology
    	symbolic key is ActionReason

    Patterns
		disable AsOfDateProcessing
		implements CRUD
		implements EffectiveDated
		implements Auditing

    Persistent Fields
		Description		is Alpha up to 100
			translatable		
		ReasonStatus 	is Numeric size 1
			States
				Active				value is 0
				Inactive			value is 1

   	Field Rules
   		Description
   			default to ActionReason

	Attach Rules
		constraint (ReasonStatus.Active)
			"ActionReasonIsInactive"
			
	Conditions
		ActionReasonEntered 
			restricted
			when (ActionReason entered)

		DescriptionEntered 
			restricted
			when (Description entered)	
			
	Derived Fields		
		DescriptionTitleMessage is a MessageField
			restricted
			"<Description>_-_ActionReason"
			
		ActionReasonTitleMessage is a MessageField
			restricted
			"<ActionReason>_-_ActionReason"	
			
		DerivedTitle is a DerivedField
			type is Alpha 200
			restricted
			if (DescriptionEntered)
				return DescriptionTitleMessage
			if (ActionReasonEntered)
				return ActionReasonTitleMessage							
			return ""
			
	Actions
		Create is a Create Action

		Update is an Update Action
				
		Delete is a Delete Action
	
		Activate is an Instance Action
			valid when (ReasonStatus.Inactive)
			Action Rules
				ReasonStatus = ReasonStatus.Active
				
		Deactivate is an Instance Action
			default label is "Inactivate"
			valid when (ReasonStatus.Active)
			Action Rules
				ReasonStatus = ReasonStatus.Inactive
